    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the sale of bottled water in plastic bottles",
        "additional_details": "We believe there is no need for selling water in bottles. There are reusable bottles people can use to fill up. We feel the sale of bottled water is completely unnecessary and it adds tons of plastic waste to an already huge environmental problem. We think individuals should use purifiers and filters if they have issues with tap water.",
        "background": "Ban the sale of all bottled water, as simple as that.",
